;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"19ff58caab8155d17ac3627d1a28ecee4a0ebd3c","tid":1728171,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47d6e292c6625f2e79aee152d1ae17fb98d5ade7","tid":1728171,"uid":88785,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"係都搞左陳怡先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"AGGER而家佢最有影響力"},{"pid":"85cd14add4d7517506a1a4e0d91f93e8ad455d95","tid":1728171,"uid":202267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:14.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"fa26990c92c6799b8b48f5ad3bd407b9f6c3d3bc","tid":1728171,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d6e292c6625f2e79aee152d1ae17fb98d5ade7","tid":1728171,"uid":88785,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"係都搞左陳怡先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"幾時開波？"},{"pid":"06d606b32b3fa43030bec87c6c0e567bfcdff31c","tid":1728171,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19ff58caab8155d17ac3627d1a28ecee4a0ebd3c","